Create ACL

standard
ip access-list standard STND-1
deny IP WILDCARD
permit any

extended
ip access-list extended EXTEND-1
deny ip IP WILDCARD host DESTINATIONHOSTIP
permit ip any any


Apply ACL to interface
Within the interface run the following
ip access-group STND-1 in/out



Delete ACL
no ip access-list type name

Show all on router
show access-lists
